as trying to beat the storm which was off to\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthe west but also right in front of me\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel4\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"23\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day25/day25pic0901.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Downhill into Salida</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day25/day25pic0902.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Downhill into Salida</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day25/day25pic0903.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Downhill into Salida</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"../img/tourdivide/day25/day25pic0904.JPG\" alt=\"Forth slide image\"\n                                                           