d me\n\t\t\t\t\t\tlater. We had pizza down the road and called it a night.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFriday, July 3 - 48.4mi Hartsel to Salida, CO\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Text by <a href=\"http://www.havingadventures.com/\">Jim O'Brien</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t. Photographs by Jim O'Brien<a href=\"https://flic.kr/s/aHsk9CwBC1\">TD on Flickr</a>.</p>"
